1eddi\u00a0&#8211; \u00cdch n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ee3i nh\u00e0&#8221;.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\">Trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh, chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p c\u00e1c th\u1eafc m\u1eafc li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch, th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi, th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c mua b\u00e1n \u0111i\u1ec7n khi h\u00f2a l\u01b0\u1edbi&#8230;<\/p>\n<p class=\"\">\u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh c\u0169ng t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng khi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi \u00e1p m\u00e1i tr\u00ean m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 h\u1ed9 gia \u0111\u00ecnh, trung t\u00e2m th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i, cao \u1ed1c&#8230;<\/p>\n<div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\">\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"\u0110\u01a1n v\u1ecb thi c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u1eafp \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi cho m\u1ed9t t\u00f2a nh\u00e0 - \u1ea2nh: QUANG KH\u1ea2I\" href=\"https:\/\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\/2019\/5\/9\/dien-mat-troi-15573774310401103485046.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-fancybox-group=\"img-lightbox\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" id=\"img_ff9d0130-7215-11e9-a080-bd923f79a53e\" class=\"lightbox-content aligncenter\" title=\"L\u1eafp \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111i\u1ec7n ra sao? - \u1ea2nh 2.\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\/thumb_w\/586\/2019\/5\/9\/dien-mat-troi-15573774310401103485046.jpg\" alt=\"L\u1eafp \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111i\u1ec7n ra sao? - \u1ea2nh 2.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\/2019\/5\/9\/dien-mat-troi-15573774310401103485046.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption ck_legend caption\">\n<p 